  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >It's as easy as riding a unicycle!</h2>Pogo3d is a technical platformer with a unique control scheme. Control your movement using only your mouse!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413620/extras/b05247aae7e4b7d59ef47b5760ea1d4c.poster.avif?t=1702317500\" width=604 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413620/extras/b05247aae7e4b7d59ef47b5760ea1d4c.webm?t=1702317500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413620/extras/b05247aae7e4b7d59ef47b5760ea1d4c.mp4?t=1702317500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Learn from your mistakes and grow!</h2>Frequent checkpoints save your progress after each obstacle. Get back into the action in less than a second.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413620/extras/4849548738f3b6239ad804542b850c6b.poster.avif?t=1702317500\" width=600 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413620/extras/4849548738f3b6239ad804542b850c6b.webm?t=1702317500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413620/extras/4849548738f3b6239ad804542b850c6b.mp4?t=1702317500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beat your head against a brick wall!</h2>Experience the main story, as well as side content and even hidden areas.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413620/extras/f7718a9cb432573f768f3661bb7cad69.poster.avif?t=1702317500\" width=600 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413620/extras/f7718a9cb432573f768f3661bb7cad69.webm?t=1702317500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413620/extras/f7718a9cb432573f768f3661bb7cad69.mp4?t=1702317500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>12 Story Chapters, each featuring unique visuals and novel gameplay<br></li><li>3 Difficulties with different rules. pick the one that's right for your skill level<br></li><li>60 standalone balloon-popping challenges. Try to beat the developer's best times<br></li><li>Custom challenge creation & sharing tools. Hide your own balloons in ridiculous places. Share with friends for maximum hilarity!</li></ul></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >It's as easy as riding a unicycle!</h2>Pogo3d is a technical platformer with a unique control scheme. Control your movement using only your mouse!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413620/extras/b05247aae7e4b7d59ef47b5760ea1d4c.poster.avif?t=1702317500\" width=604 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413620/extras/b05247aae7e4b7d59ef47b5760ea1d4c.webm?t=1702317500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413620/extras/b05247aae7e4b7d59ef47b5760ea1d4c.mp4?t=1702317500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Learn from your mistakes and grow!</h2>Frequent checkpoints save your progress after each obstacle. Get back into the action in less than a second.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413620/extras/4849548738f3b6239ad804542b850c6b.poster.avif?t=1702317500\" width=600 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413620/extras/4849548738f3b6239ad804542b850c6b.webm?t=1702317500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413620/extras/4849548738f3b6239ad804542b850c6b.mp4?t=1702317500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beat your head against a brick wall!</h2>Experience the main story, as well as side content and even hidden areas.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2413620/extras/f7718a9cb432573f768f3661bb7cad69.poster.avif?t=1702317500\" width=600 height=276 >